title: Winds of Winter release date announced?
subtitle: Before Jan 1, 2025
rules_primary: If George R.R. Martin has announced a release date for The Winds of Winter before Jan 1, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.

title: Zyn banned in the United States in 2024
rules_primary: If Zyn nicotine pouches have been banned by the U.S. federal government by Dec 31, 2024, then the market resolves to Yes.
rules_secondary: NOTE: originally the product filing used the term nicotine 'pouch' and 'patch' interchangeably. This has been changed in the rules. This contract refers to nicotine pouches.

title: Will MIT leave her position as univeristy president?
subtitle: MIT :: Sally Kornbluth
rules_primary: If it is announced that the president of MIT will leave by Dec 31, 2024, then the market resolves to Yes.
rules_secondary: It is sufficient for the announcement to have been made even if the transition proper has not occurred by <date> to be encompassed within the Payout Criterion.

title: Will room-temperature superconductivity be reported by a major peer-reviewed journal?
subtitle: By Dec 31, 2024
rules_primary: If an eligible peer-reviewed journal publishes research that reports that a material is room-temperature superconductive (it has a critical temperature greater than room temperature, exhibits 10^-10 ohm-cm electrical resistivity or less, and exhibits the Meissner effect), then the market resolves to Yes.
rules_secondary: Eligible journals include those in the first quartile ("Q1") of SJR's condensed matter physics journals or any journal above a 1.0 SJR ranking.
